Kudos - Local Recommendations

Have you ever been traveling and wished you knew what the locals know? Explore new areas and give Kudos to things you like the most. 

Discover everything from local hangouts to the best neighborhood restaurants with Kudos. 

Help build the community by recommending your own favorites as you go. 

Simply snap a photo, add a title - and post! 

Features: 

• Find top local attractions close to you at any given time 
• Find local attractions in other cities 
• Give kudos! 
• Add your own recommendations 
• Search for local top recommendations